      "text": "優、待ってくれ！　優ーー！\n……どうして、こんなことになってしまったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ wait! Yu—!\n…How did it end up like this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Several Weeks Earlier",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.534059302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
